# ============================================
# The following are NOT set here.
# They are configured as Supabase Edge Function secrets.
# See SETUP_GUIDE.md for instructions.
# ============================================
#
# WHATSAPP_ACCESS_TOKEN  → From Meta Developer Console (WhatsApp API token)
# WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN  → You create this (any random string for webhook verification)
#
# Set them via CLI:
#   supabase secrets set WHATSAPP_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-token-here
#   supabase secrets set WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN=your-verify-token-here
